window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Lance, last living dragon mage of the northern province has become truly formidable.</b></p> <p>His followers have grown, his village has expanded, and his lovely group of arcanist companions have become deadly in their own right. Now, with his [s-rank] abilities fully realized, there are few in the realm who can match his might.</p> <p>But there are those who will try.</p> <p>The Kel’sar clan has caught wind of Lance’s advancements, and they intend on sending Oracle’s mightiest to extinguish his flames. That may not even be his greatest threat though…for in the ravelands, a certain necromancer dabbles in powers beyond her comprehension...and the remains of a dead god begins to stir.</p> <p><i>This novel contains progression, harem, and LitRPG elements. It is intended for mature audiences.</i></p>"; 
